item.description:
You can download the latest binary from here or from the GitHub release page.
Linux (x64) 1.) Download the latest version: zsd-linux-v1.2.0.tgz
2.) Run it: ./zsd &lt;FILE&gt; &lt;ACTION&gt;
FreeBSD (x64) 1.) Download the latest version: zsd-freebsd-v1.2.0.tgz
2.) Run it: ./zsd &lt;FILE&gt; &lt;ACTION&gt;
Solaris (x64) 1.) Download the latest version: zsd-solaris-v1.2.0.tgz
2.) Run it: ./zsd &lt;FILE&gt; &lt;ACTION&gt;
Mac OS (x64) 1.) Download the latest version: zsd-darwin-v1.
